<html>
    <head>
        <title>Revitalize Proc Calculator</title>
        <script src="https://ajax.googleapis.com/ajax/libs/jquery/2.1.3/jquery.min.js"></script>
        <script src="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.13.0/jquery-ui.js"></script>
        <link rel="stylesheet" type="text/css" href="/stylesheets/main.css" />
        <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://code.jquery.com/ui/1.13.0/themes/base/jquery-ui.css">
        <script type="text/javascript" src="/scripts/index.js"></script>
    </head>
    <body>
        <div class="box">
            <div class="title">
                Revitalize Proc Calculator
            </div>
            <div class="inputs">
                <div class="text-inputs">
                    <div class="log-input-container">
                        <label for="log-input">Log URL</label>
                        <input type="text" id="log-input" name="log-input" autocomplete="on"/>
                    </div>
                    <div class="api-key-input-container">
                        <label for="api-key">API Key</label>
                        <div class="api-input-field">
                            <input type="text" id="api-key-input" name="api-key-input"/>
                            <div class="input-explanation">
                                <a id="api-key-more-info" href="#">What is this?</a>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                    </div>
                </div>
                <div class="button-container">
                    <input type="button" id="calculate" value="Calculate" onclick="calculate()"/>
                </div>
            </div>
        </div>
        <div id="results">
        </div>
        <div class="hover_bkgr_fricc">
            <span class="helper"></span>
            <div>
                <div class="popupCloseButton">&times;</div>
                <p>The API key allows you to access Warcraft Logs data. I would give you my own, but if it's used too frequently it gets rejected.</p>
                <p>Go to the bottom of <a target="_blank" href="https://classic.warcraftlogs.com/profile">https://classic.warcraftlogs.com/profile</a> and follow the V1 instructions to get a "V1 Client Key" which is what you want to input here.</p>
            </div>
        </div>
    </body>
</html>